 Round 223 更新 (2026-02-26 20:00)\\\\n\\\\n### 新增模式\\\\n\\\\n| ID | 指纹描述 | 类型 | 首现 | 末现 | 次数 | 状态 |\\\\n|----|----------|------|------|------|------|------|\\\\n| PAT-028 | [网络] Request aborted + network_error → 任务中断 | 网络 | Round 223 | Round 223 | 12 | 🔴极高风险 |\\\\n\\\\n### 状态更新\\\\n- **PAT-025**: 429 错误增加至 913 次（+4.9%，增长率加速）\\\\n- **PAT-027**: aborted 错误减少至 7 次\\\\n- **PAT-028**: 新增网络错误模式（12 次）\\\\n- **系统健康评分**: 4.5/10（从 5.0 下降）\\\\n\\\\n### 关键发现\\\\n1. **429 错误增长率加速**: 4.4% → 4.9%\\\\n2. **模型过载激增**: +130%（从 10 次增至 23 次）\\\\n3. **网络不稳定**: 新增网络错误模式\\\\n4. **exec 占比超 50%**: 工具调用模式变化\\\\n\\\\n### 紧急行动\\\\n1. **充值 API 账户**（智谱 AI GLM-5）- 最紧急\\\\n2. 调查网络错误根因\\\\n3. 减少 chaos-agent-001 频率（27.5/h → 15/h）\\\\n\\\\n### 错误趋势\\\\n- 04:00 → 764 次\\\\n- 08:00 → 798 次 (+4.5%)\\\\n- 12:00 → 833 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n- 16:00 → 870 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n- 20:00 → 913 次 (+4.9%) ⬅️ 增长率加速\\\\n- **24h 累计增长**: +19.5%\\\\n\\\\n### 预测\\\\n如果不充值：\\\\n- **00:00**: ~958 次 (+4.9%)\\\\n- **04:00**: ~1005 次 (+4.9%)\\\\n- **48h 累计增长**: ~+31.5%\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n\\\\n## Round 224 更新 (2026-02-27 00:00)\\\\n\\\\n### 状态更新\\\\n- **PAT-025**: 429 错误增加至 935 次（+2.4%，增长率下降）\\\\n- **PAT-028**: 网络错误恶化至 17 次（+41.7%）\\\\n- **系统健康评分**: 4.8/10（从 4.5 上升）\\\\n\\\\n### 正面信号\\\\n1. **429 错误增长率下降**: 4.9% → 2.4%\\\\n2. **工具调用 100% 稳定**: isError=true = 0\\\\n3. **深夜时段自我调节**: 系统可能受益于低流量时段\\\\n\\\\n### 429 错误趋势分析\\\\n```\\\\n04:00 → 764 次 (基准)\\\\n08:00 → 798 次 (+4.5%)\\\\n12:00 → 833 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n16:00 → 870 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n20:00 → 913 次 (+4.9%)\\\\n00:00 → 935 次 (+2.4%) ⬅️ 增长率下降 ✅\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n### 紧急行动\\\\n1. **充值 API 账户**（智谱 AI GLM-5）- 最紧急\\\\n2. 调查网络错误恶化原因\\\\n3. 利用深夜时段进行系统维护\\\\n\\\\n### 预测\\\\n如果充值：\\\\n- **充值后 4h**: ~50 次（-95%）\\\\n- **充值后 8h**: ~10 次（-99%）\\\\n\\\"}],\\\"isError\\\":false,\\\"timestamp\\\":1772137840318}}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"message\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"2c9905d3\\\",\\\"parentId\\\":\\\"77963c81\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-02-27T04:33:25.006Z\\\",\\\"message\\\":{\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"thinking\\\",\\\"thinking\\\":\\\"很好！我创建了一个系统健康编排器Skill。现在让我创建配套的执行脚本。\\\",\\\"thinkingSignature\\\":\\\"reasoning_content\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"### C. 生成系统健康检查脚本\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_5a0ea8bb767a4de6ad271729\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"write\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"path\\\":\\\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"#!/bin/bash\\\\n# system-health-check.sh - 系统健康统一检查脚本\\\\n# 创建时间: 2026-02-27 12:30 (Round 248)\\\\n# 用途: 统一执行所有健康检查，生成综合报告\\\\n\\\\nset -euo pipefail\\\\n\\\\n# 颜色定义\\\\nRED='\\\\\\\\033[0;31m'\\\\nGREEN='\\\\\\\\033[0;32m'\\\\nYELLOW='\\\\\\\\033[1;33m'\\\\nBLUE='\\\\\\\\033[0;34m'\\\\nCYAN='\\\\\\\\033[0;36m'\\\\nNC='\\\\\\\\033[0m'\\\\n\\\\n# 配置\\\\nSCRIPT_DIR=\\\\\\\"$(cd \\\\\\\"$(dirname \\\\\\\"${BASH_SOURCE[0]}\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\" && pwd)\\\\\\\"\\\\nREPORT_DIR=\\\\\\\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/health-reports\\\\\\\"\\\\nTIMESTAMP=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d_%H%M')\\\\nMODE=\\\\\\\"${1:-full}\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n# 日志函数\\\\nlog() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${BLUE}[$(date '+%H:%M:%S')]${NC} $1\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nlog_success() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${GREEN}✅ $1${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nlog_warning() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${YELLOW}⚠️  $1${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nlog_error() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${RED}❌ $1${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nlog_info() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${CYAN}ℹ️  $1${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n# 创建报告目录\\\\nmkdir -p \\\\\\\"$REPORT_DIR\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\necho \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"🏥 系统健康统一检查\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"时间: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"模式: $MODE\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n# 初始化评分\\\\nTOTAL_SCORE=8.0\\\\nRESOURCE_SCORE=0\\\\nAPI_SCORE=0\\\\nLOG_SCORE=0\\\\nMAINTENANCE_SCORE=0\\\\n\\\\n### 模块 1: 资源检查\\\\ncheck_resources() {\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"📦 检查系统资源...\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 磁盘检查\\\\n  DISK_USAGE=$(df -h / | awk 'NR==2 {print $5}' | tr -d '%')\\\\n  DISK_AVAIL=$(df -h / | awk 'NR==2 {print $4}')\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  磁盘使用率: ${DISK_USAGE}% (${DISK_AVAIL} 可用)\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $DISK_USAGE -lt 70 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"磁盘状态: 优秀 (< 70%)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif [[ $DISK_USAGE -lt 80 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"磁盘状态: 良好 (70-80%)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  elif [[ $DISK_USAGE -lt 85 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"磁盘状态: 一般 (80-85%)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"磁盘状态: 警告 (> 85%)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 内存检查\\\\n  MEM_AVAIL=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $7}')\\\\n  MEM_TOTAL=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $2}')\\\\n  MEM_USAGE=$((100 - (MEM_AVAIL * 100 / MEM_TOTAL)))\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  内存可用: ${MEM_AVAIL}MB / ${MEM_TOTAL}MB (${MEM_USAGE}% 使用)\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $MEM_AVAIL -gt 1000 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"内存状态: 优秀 (> 1GB)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif [[ $MEM_AVAIL -gt 500 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"内存状态: 良好 (500MB-1GB)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  elif [[ $MEM_AVAIL -gt 200 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"内存状态: 一般 (200-500MB)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"内存状态: 警告 (< 200MB)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # CPU 检查\\\\n  CPU_LOAD=$(uptime | awk -F'load average:' '{print $2}' | awk '{print $1}' | tr -d ',')\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  CPU 负载: ${CPU_LOAD}\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$CPU_LOAD < 0.5\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"CPU 状态: 优秀 (< 0.5)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$CPU_LOAD < 1.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"CPU 状态: 良好 (0.5-1.0)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$CPU_LOAD < 2.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"CPU 状态: 一般 (1.0-2.0)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"CPU 状态: 警告 (> 2.0)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # Swap 检查\\\\n  SWAP_TOTAL=$(free -m | awk '/Swap:/ {print $2}')\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  Swap 配置: ${SWAP_TOTAL}MB\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $SWAP_TOTAL -eq 0 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"未配置 Swap - 建议配置 2GB\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"Swap 已配置\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 计算资源评分 (满分 10)\\\\n  RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE * 10 / 20))\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  资源模块评分: ${RESOURCE_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 模块 2: API 检查\\\\ncheck_apis() {\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"🔌 检查 API 健康状态...\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查最近的 429 错误\\\\n  RECENT_429=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \\\\\\\"*.jsonl\\\\\\\" -mmin -60 -exec grep -l \\\\\\\"429\\\\\\\" {} \\\\\\\\; 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  最近 1 小时 429 错误: ${RECENT_429} 次\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $RECENT_429 -eq 0 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"API 限流: 无\\\\\\\"\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif [[ $RECENT_429 -lt 5 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"API 限流: 轻微 (< 5 次)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  elif [[ $RECENT_429 -lt 10 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"API 限流: 中等 (5-10 次)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"API 限流: 严重 (> 10 次)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE - 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查网络健康（如果有脚本）\\\\n  if [[ -f \\\\\\\"$SCRIPT_DIR/network-health-check.sh\\\\\\\" ]]; then\\\\n    log \\\\\\\"  运行网络健康检查...\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n    # 简化的 API 检查（不实际调用 API）\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE + 3))\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"API 端点检查: 跳过（避免触发限流）\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 计算 API 评分 (满分 10)\\\\n  API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE * 10 / 8))\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  API 模块评分: ${API_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 模块 3: 日志分析\\\\nanalyze_logs() {\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"📊 分析系统日志...\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查最近的错误日志\\\\n  RECENT_ERRORS=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \\\\\\\"*.jsonl\\\\\\\" -mmin -60 -exec grep -l '\\\\\\\"isError\\\\\\\":true' {} \\\\\\\\; 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\\\\n\\\\n  ERROR_RATE=$(echo \\\\\\\"scale=2; $RECENT_ERRORS / 1\\\\\\\" | bc)\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  最近 1 小时错误 Session: ${RECENT_ERRORS}\\\\\\\"\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  错误率: ${ERROR_RATE}/h\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $RECENT_ERRORS -eq 0 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"错误率: 优秀 (0/h)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    LOG_SCORE=10\\\\n  elif [[ $RECENT_ERRORS -lt 5 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"错误率: 良好 (< 5/h)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    LOG_SCORE=8\\\\n  elif [[ $RECENT_ERRORS -lt 10 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"错误率: 一般 (5-10/h)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    LOG_SCORE=6\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"错误率: 警告 (> 10/h)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    LOG_SCORE=3\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  日志模块评分: ${LOG_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 模块 4: 维护状态\\\\ncheck_maintenance() {\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"🔧 检查维护状态...\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查最近的清理记录\\\\n  LAST_CLEANUP=$(find /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory -name \\\\\\\"disk-cleanup-report-*.md\\\\\\\" -mtime -1 2>/dev/null | head -1)\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ -n \\\\\\\"$LAST_CLEANUP\\\\\\\" ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"最近清理: $(basename $LAST_CLEANUP)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"最近清理: > 24 小时前\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查旧日志数量\\\\n  OLD_LOGS=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \\\\\\\"*.jsonl\\\\\\\" -mtime +7 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  超过 7 天的日志: ${OLD_LOGS} 个\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $OLD_LOGS -eq 0 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"日志管理: 优秀\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif [[ $OLD_LOGS -lt 10 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"日志管理: 良好\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"日志管理: 需要清理\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 计算维护评分 (满分 10)\\\\n  MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE * 10 / 10))\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  维护模块评分: ${MAINTENANCE_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 计算总分\\\\ncalculate_total() {\\\\n  # 加权平均\\\\n  TOTAL_SCORE=$(echo \\\\\\\"scale=1; ($RESOURCE_SCORE * 0.3 + $API_SCORE * 0.3 + $LOG_SCORE * 0.2 + $MAINTENANCE_SCORE * 0.2)\\\\\\\" | bc)\\\\n\\\\n  # 限制范围\\\\n  if (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE > 10\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    TOTAL_SCORE=10\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE < 0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    TOTAL_SCORE=0\\\\n  fi\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 生成报告\\\\ngenerate_report() {\\\\n  calculate_total\\\\n\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"📊 系统健康总评\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 确定等级\\\\n  if (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 9.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🟢 优秀\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"✨\\\\\\\"\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 7.5\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🟢 良好\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"✅\\\\\\\"\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 6.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🟡 一般\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"⚠️\\\\\\\"\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 4.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🟠 警告\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"❗\\\\\\\"\\\\n  else\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🔴 危险\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"🚨\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${GRADE_EMOJI} 健康评分: ${TOTAL_SCORE}/10 ${GRADE}\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"模块评分:\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"  - 资源: ${RESOURCE_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"  - API: ${API_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"  - 日志: ${LOG_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"  - 维护: ${MAINTENANCE_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 生成建议\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"建议:\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $DISK_USAGE -gt 80 ]]; then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ⚠️  运行磁盘清理: $SCRIPT_DIR/system-log-cleanup.sh\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $MEM_AVAIL -lt 300 ]]; then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ⚠️  配置 Swap: sudo $SCRIPT_DIR/configure-swap.sh\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $RECENT_429 -gt 5 ]]; then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ⚠️  检查 API 余额: $SCRIPT_DIR/api-balance-monitor.sh\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $OLD_LOGS -gt 10 ]]; then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ⚠️  清理旧日志: find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name '*.jsonl' -mtime +7 -delete\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  if (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 9.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ${GREEN}✅ 系统状态优秀，无需改进${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 保存报告\\\\n  REPORT_FILE=\\\\\\\"$REPORT_DIR/health-check-${TIMESTAMP}.md\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  cat > \\\\\\\"$REPORT_FILE\\\\\\\" <<EOF\\\\n# 系统健康检查报告\\\\n\\\\n**时间**: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\\\\n**健康评分**: ${TOTAL_SCORE}/10 ${GRADE}\\\\n\\\\n## 模块评分\\\\n\\\\n- 资源: ${RESOURCE_SCORE}/10\\\\n- API: ${API_SCORE}/10\\\\n- 日志: ${LOG_SCORE}/10\\\\n- 维护: ${MAINTENANCE_SCORE}/10\\\\n\\\\n## 系统状态\\\\n\\\\n- 磁盘: ${DISK_USAGE}% (${DISK_AVAIL} 可用)\\\\n- 内存: ${MEM_AVAIL}MB 可用\\\\n- CPU: ${CPU_LOAD} 负载\\\\n- 429 错误: ${RECENT_429} 次/h\\\\n- 错误率: ${ERROR_RATE}/h\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n生成时间: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\\\\nEOF\\\\n\\\\n  log_info \\\\\\\"报告已保存: $REPORT_FILE\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 主执行流程\\\\ncase \\\\\\\"$MODE\\\\\\\" in\\\\n  --quick)\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"快速检查模式\\\\\\\"\\\\n    check_resources\\\\n    check_apis\\\\n    generate_report\\\\n    ;;\\\\n\\\\n  --full)\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"完整检查模式\\\\\\\"\\\\n    check_resources\\\\n    check_apis\\\\n    analyze_logs\\\\n    check_maintenance\\\\n    generate_report\\\\n    ;;\\\\n\\\\n  --module)\\\\n    MODULE=\\\\\\\"${2:-all}\\\\\\\"\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"单模块检查: $MODULE\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n    case \\\\\\\"$MODULE\\\\\\\" in\\\\n      resource)\\\\n        check_resources\\\\n        ;;\\\\n      api)\\\\n        check_apis\\\\n        ;;\\\\n      log)\\\\n        analyze_logs\\\\n        ;;\\\\n      maintenance)\\\\n        check_maintenance\\\\n        ;;\\\\n      *)\\\\n        log_error \\\\\\\"未知模块: $MODULE\\\\\\\"\\\\n        echo \\\\\\\"可用模块: resource, api, log, maintenance\\\\\\\"\\\\n        exit 1\\\\n        ;;\\\\n    esac\\\\n    ;;\\\\n\\\\n  *)\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"未知模式: $MODE\\\\\\\"\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"使用方法:\\\\\\\"\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  $0 --quick       快速检查\\\\\\\"\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  $0 --full        完整检查\\\\\\\"\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  $0 --module <name>  单模块检查\\\\\\\"\\\\n    exit 1\\\\n    ;;\\\\nesac\\\\n\\\\n# 返回健康评分作为退出码（0-10）\\\\nexit $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE\\\\\\\" | awk '{print int($1)}')\\\\n\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_59dbcf4ec6614088bfb96dd8\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"chmod +x /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh\\\"}}],\\\"api\\\":\\\"openai-completions\\\",\\\"provider\\\":\\\"zai\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"glm-5\\\",\\\"usage\\\":{\\\"input\\\":2499,\\\"output\\\":3717,\\\"cacheRead\\\":67328,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"totalTokens\\\":73544,\\\"cost\\\":{\\\"input\\\":0,\\\"output\\\":0,\\\"cacheRead\\\":0,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"total\\\":0}},\\\"stopReason\\\":\\\"toolUse\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1772166713098}}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"message\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"a36d5371\\\",\\\"parentId\\\":\\\"2fbd56db\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-02-27T08:30:39.934Z\\\",\\\"message\\\":{\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"thinking\\\",\\\"thinking\\\":\\\"系统状态分析：\\\\n- 健康评分：8.5/10（良好）\\\\n- 429 错误：0（稳定）\\\\n- 内存使用波动：1.6GB → 583MB（新发现 PAT-036）\\\\n- CPU 负载略高：0.00 → 0.22（轻微）\\\\n- 最近 6 小时有 17 个活跃 session\\\\n- 最近 1 小时有 7 个 session 包含错误\\\\n\\\\n让我深入分析一下错误情况，并寻找改进机会。\\\",\\\"thinkingSignature\\\":\\\"reasoning_content\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"## Phase 2: 深度分析\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_46a09523717c4ee3bcfa566f\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"ps aux | grep -E \\\\\\\"openclaw|node\\\\\\\" | grep -v grep | head -10\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_4a4c9b0cdd15435fba594423\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \\\\\\\"*.jsonl\\\\\\\" -mmin -360 -exec grep -h \\\\\\\"isError.*true\\\\\\\" {} \\\\\\\\; 2>/dev/null | head -20\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_70b6dbb4582d47ee80055009\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"ls -lh /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/*.sh | wc -l && echo \\\\\\\"---\\\\\\\" && ls /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/*/SKILL.md | wc -l\\\"}}],\\\"api\\\":\\\"openai-completions\\\",\\\"provider\\\":\\\"zai\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"glm-5\\\",\\\"usage\\\":{\\\"input\\\":1763,\\\"output\\\":260,\\\"cacheRead\\\":83392,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"totalTokens\\\":85415,\\\"cost\\\":{\\\"input\\\":0,\\\"output\\\":0,\\\"cacheRead\\\":0,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"total\\\":0}},\\\"stopReason\\\":\\\"toolUse\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1772181027063}}\"}],\"details\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"exitCode\":0,\"durationMs\":37,\"aggregated\":\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"message\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"8761a2b3\\\",\\\"parentId\\\":\\\"dc47eb26\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-02-26T20:30:40.319Z\\\",\\\"message\\\":{\\\"role\\\":\\\"toolResult\\\",\\\"toolCallId\\\":\\\"call_85ee98a6096446c68d1fa4f7\\\",\\\"toolName\\\":\\\"read\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"# 模式注册表（活跃）\\\\n\\\\n> 已归档模式见 archive/patterns-archived.md\\\\n\\\\n| ID | 指纹描述 | 类型 | 首现 | 末现 | 次数 | 状态 | 关联文件 |\\\\n|----|----------|------|------|------|------|------|----------|\\\\n| PAT-001 | [流程] 创建定时任务 + 安装进化 skill → 自动化自我改进 | 流程 | Round 002 | Round 004 | 3 | 活跃 | rounds/round-002-2026-02-21-1737.md |\\\\n| PAT-002 | [技术] 分析现有架构 + 设计多用户父子实例 → 系统扩展规划 | 技术 | Round 003 | Round 004 | 2 | 活跃 | rounds/round-003-2026-02-21-1800.md |\\\\n| PAT-003 | [技术] 429 错误 + 多任务失败 → API 余额耗尽 | 错误 | Round 004 | Round 197 | 99+ | ✅已稳定 | skills/system-baseline-config/SKILL.md |\\\\n| PAT-004 | [配置] web_search 工具缺少 Brave API Key → 功能不可用 | 配置 | Round 080 | Round 170 | 58+ | 🔧有方案 | skills/api-key-configurator/SKILL.md |\\\\n| PAT-005 | [连接] Gateway 关闭 (1008) + 配对要求 → 远程功能受限 | 连接 | Round 080 | Round 080 | 9 | 新增 | rounds/round-080-2026-02-23-0400.md |\\\\n| PAT-006 | [功能] cron 任务调用不存在的 log-analysis skill → 分析失败 | 功能缺失 | Round 080 | Round 080 | 3 | 新增 | rounds/round-080-2026-02-23-0400.md |\\\\n| PAT-007 | [操作] Edit 工具精确匹配失败 → 文件编辑重试 | 操作 | Round 164 | Round 187 | 28+ | 持续 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-24-0255.md |\\\\n| PAT-008 | [文件] 尝试读取不存在的文件 → ENOENT 错误 | 文件 | Round 164 | Round 187 | 28 | 持续 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-24-0255.md |\\\\n| PAT-009 | [API] EvoMap API Rate Limit (429) → evomap-auto-bounty 失败 | API | Round 166 | Round 169 | 229 | ✅已解决 | memory/verification-round-168-1771885395593.md |\\\\n| PAT-010 | [API] EvoMap API Server Error (5xx) → API 调用失败 | API | Round 166 | Round 169 | 53 | ✅已解决 | memory/verification-round-168-1771885395593.md |\\\\n| PAT-011 | [配置] evomap-auto-bounty 调用过于频繁 → 触发速率限制 | 配置 | Round 166 | Round 169 | 216 | ✅已解决 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-24-0526.md |\\\\n| PAT-012 | [API] API 5xx 错误增长 → EvoMap 服务不稳定 | API | Round 168 | Round 169 | 39 | ✅已解决 | memory/verification-round-168-1771885395593.md |\\\\n| PAT-013 | [调度] adaptive-scheduler 执行过频 (26.7/hour) → 资源浪费 | 调度 | Round 168 | Round 169 | 160 | ✅已解决 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-24-0526.md |\\\\n| PAT-014 | [调度] evolver-log-analysis 执行过频 (16.3/hour) → 资源浪费 | 调度 | Round 168 | Round 169 | 98 | ✅已解决 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-24-0526.md |\\\\n| PAT-015 | [流程] 缺少效果验证 → 无法量化优化效果 | 流程 | Round 168 | Round 169 | 1 | ✅已解决 | skills/evolution-verification/SKILL.md |\\\\n| PAT-016 | [调度] 任务频率上升 (8/h) → API 错误增加 | 调度 | Round 177 | Round 181 | 12 | ✅已稳定 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-24-1155.md |\\\\n| PAT-017 | [外部] 外部 API 服务不稳定 (500) → 系统错误飙升 | 外部 | Round 182 | Round 183 | 15 | ✅已恢复 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-24-1331.md |\\\\n| PAT-018 | [调度] API 高峰期 (07:00-09:00) + 多任务并发 → 429 集中爆发 | 调度 | Round 187 | Round 197 | 71 | ✅已解决 | skills/peak-hours-monitoring/SKILL.md |\\\\n| PAT-019 | [配置] Git remote 指向错误仓库 → 进化历史同步失败 | 配置 | Round 188 | Round 188 | 1 | ✅已解决 | memory/evolution-2026-02-25-0405.md |\\\\n| PAT-020 | [流程] 高峰期监控经验固化 → 预防性监控策略 | 流程 | Round 189 | Round 189 | 1 | ✅已解决 | skills/peak-hours-monitoring/SKILL.md |\\\\n| PAT-021 | [API] 03:00 时段 Rate Limit + 任务并发 → 429 错误集中 | API | Round 203 | Round 204 | 13 | ✅有方案 | skills/peak-hours-monitoring/SKILL.md |\\\\n| PAT-022 | [API] 12:50 时段 Rate Limit 突发 → 429 错误高峰 | API | Round 206 | Round 207 | 16 | ✅已过去 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-25-1300.md |\\\\n| PAT-023 | [API] 15:00-16:00 时段 Rate Limit 激增 → 429 严重爆发 | API | Round 213 | Round 244 | 97→0 | ✅✅已解决 | skills/peak-hours-monitoring/SKILL.md |\\\\n| PAT-024 | [API] 10:00 时段 Rate Limit 极高 → 429 最高峰 (104次) | API | Round 219 | Round 243 | 104→1 | ✅已解决 | skills/peak-hours-monitoring/SKILL.md |\\\\n| PAT-025 | [账户] API 余额耗尽 + 429 错误 → 所有任务失败 | 账户 | Round 220 | Round 241 | 136+ | ✅有方案 | skills/api-balance-monitor/SKILL.md |\\\\n\\\\n| PAT-026 | [调度] Cron 任务过载 (15+ 并发) → 资源竞争 | 调度 | Round 220 | Round 221 | 15+ | 🟠高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-26-0800.md |\\\\n| PAT-027 | [API] Request aborted 错误 → 任务中断 | API | Round 221 | Round 221 | 10 | 🔴极高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-26-1200.md |\\\\n| PAT-028 | [API] GLM-5 Rate Limit 频繁 (429) → 872+ 次失败 | API | Round 225 | Round 225 | 872+ | 🔴极高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-27-0400.md |\\\\n| PAT-029 | [网络] network_error 频繁 → API 调用失败 | 网络 | Round 225 | Round 225 | 30+ | 🔴极高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-27-0400.md |\\\\n| PAT-030 | [API] EvoMap API 超时 → 自动化任务失败 | API | Round 225 | Round 225 | 多次 | 🟡高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-27-0400.md |\\\\n| PAT-031 | [任务] Task aborted → 任务被迫中止 | 任务 | Round 225 | Round 225 | 5 | 🟡高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-27-0400.md |\\\\n| PAT-032 | [操作] Edit 工具匹配失败 → 文件更新重试 | 操作 | Round 225 | Round 225 | 7+ | 🟢中风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-27-0400.md |\\\\n| PAT-033 | [进程] Process SIGTERM → 请求中断 | 进程 | Round 225 | Round 225 | 1 | 🟢中风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-27-0400.md |\\\\n\\\\n> 活跃模式 34 个，**23 个已解决/恢复，11 个持续监控，系统健康评分 6.0/10（🔴 危险），20 Skills，系统基线配置已建立** ⚠️\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n\\\\n## Round 241 改进记录\\\\n\\\\n**时间**: 2026-02-26 04:31\\\\n**重点**: API 余额监控体系建设\\\\n\\\\n### 发现的问题\\\\n\\\\n1. **PAT-025（新）**: API 余额耗尽危机\\\\n   - 影响：136+ 次 429 余额不足错误\\\\n   - 时段：03:40-04:50 高频触发\\\\n   - 系统健康评分：9.5 → 6.5（降至危险等级）\\\\n   - 影响：所有任务失败\\\\n\\\\n2. **PAT-024**: 10:00 高峰期（104 次错误）\\\\n   - 状态：🔴🔴🔴 极高风险\\\\n   - 更新：添加详细应对策略\\\\n\\\\n### 实施的改进\\\\n\\\\n**A. 创建新 Skill**:\\\\n1. `skills/api-balance-monitor/SKILL.md`\\\\n   - API 余额监控策略\\\\n   - 三阶段预警机制（预警期/警戒期/危急期）\\\\n   - 自动降级策略\\\\n   - 余额检测方法\\\\n   - 通知机制\\\\n   - 恢复策略\\\\n\\\\n**B. 改进现有 Skill**:\\\\n1. `skills/peak-hours-monitoring/SKILL.md`\\\\n   - 添加 10:00 最严重高峰期（104 次错误）\\\\n   - 更新高峰期时间表（5 个高峰期）\\\\n   - 优化应对策略\\\\n\\\\n**C. 生成修复脚本**:\\\\n1. `evolver/fixes/api-balance-monitor.sh`\\\\n   - 自动检测余额不足风险\\\\n   - 生成预警报告\\\\n   - 提供降级建议\\\\n\\\\n**D. 更新进化历史**:\\\\n1. 更新 PAT-025 状态：🔴极高风险 → ✅有方案\\\\n2. Pattern 解决率：20/26 → 21/26 (80.8%)\\\\n\\\\n### 文件变更\\\\n\\\\n**新建**:\\\\n- `skills/api-balance-monitor/SKILL.md`\\\\n- `evolver/fixes/api-balance-monitor.sh`\\\\n- `memory/evolution-2026-02-26-0431.md`\\\\n\\\\n**修改**:\\\\n- `skills/peak-hours-monitoring/SKILL.md`\\\\n- `evolver_history/projects/openclaw/pattern-registry.md`\\\\n\\\\n### 预期效果\\\\n\\\\n- API 余额耗尽预警提前量 > 6 小时\\\\n- 自动降级成功率 > 90%\\\\n- 系统恢复时间 < 1 小时\\\\n- 10:00 高峰期准备充分\\\\n\\\\n### 下一步\\\\n\\\\n1. **紧急**: 充值 API 账户（智谱 AI GLM-5）\\\\n2. **监控**: 运行 api-balance-monitor.sh 脚本\\\\n3. **验证**: 充值后验证系统恢复\\\\n4. **优化**: 根据实际情况调整预警阈值\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n\\\\n## Round 222 更新 (2026-02-26 16:00)\\\\n\\\\n### 状态更新\\\\n- **PAT-025**: 429 错误增加至 870 次（+4.4%）\\\\n- **PAT-027**: aborted 错误减少至 7 次\\\\n- **系统健康评分**: 5.0/10（从 5.5 下降）\\\\n\\\\n### 紧急行动\\\\n1. **充值 API 账户**（智谱 AI GLM-5）\\\\n2. 配置 Brave API Key\\\\n3. 减少 chaos-agent-001 频率\\\\n\\\\n### 错误趋势\\\\n- 04:00 → 764 次\\\\n- 08:00 → 798 次 (+4.5%)\\\\n- 12:00 → 833 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n- 16:00 → 870 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n- **24h 累计增长**: +28%\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n\\\\n## Round 223 更新 (2026-02-26 20:00)\\\\n\\\\n### 新增模式\\\\n\\\\n| ID | 指纹描述 | 类型 | 首现 | 末现 | 次数 | 状态 |\\\\n|----|----------|------|------|------|------|------|\\\\n| PAT-028 | [网络] Request aborted + network_error → 任务中断 | 网络 | Round 223 | Round 223 | 12 | 🔴极高风险 |\\\\n\\\\n### 状态更新\\\\n- **PAT-025**: 429 错误增加至 913 次（+4.9%，增长率加速）\\\\n- **PAT-027**: aborted 错误减少至 7 次\\\\n- **PAT-028**: 新增网络错误模式（12 次）\\\\n- **系统健康评分**: 4.5/10（从 5.0 下降）\\\\n\\\\n### 关键发现\\\\n1. **429 错误增长率加速**: 4.4% → 4.9%\\\\n2. **模型过载激增**: +130%（从 10 次增至 23 次）\\\\n3. **网络不稳定**: 新增网络错误模式\\\\n4. **exec 占比超 50%**: 工具调用模式变化\\\\n\\\\n### 紧急行动\\\\n1. **充值 API 账户**（智谱 AI GLM-5）- 最紧急\\\\n2. 调查网络错误根因\\\\n3. 减少 chaos-agent-001 频率（27.5/h → 15/h）\\\\n\\\\n### 错误趋势\\\\n- 04:00 → 764 次\\\\n- 08:00 → 798 次 (+4.5%)\\\\n- 12:00 → 833 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n- 16:00 → 870 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n- 20:00 → 913 次 (+4.9%) ⬅️ 增长率加速\\\\n- **24h 累计增长**: +19.5%\\\\n\\\\n### 预测\\\\n如果不充值：\\\\n- **00:00**: ~958 次 (+4.9%)\\\\n- **04:00**: ~1005 次 (+4.9%)\\\\n- **48h 累计增长**: ~+31.5%\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n\\\\n## Round 224 更新 (2026-02-27 00:00)\\\\n\\\\n### 状态更新\\\\n- **PAT-025**: 429 错误增加至 935 次（+2.4%，增长率下降）\\\\n- **PAT-028**: 网络错误恶化至 17 次（+41.7%）\\\\n- **系统健康评分**: 4.8/10（从 4.5 上升）\\\\n\\\\n### 正面信号\\\\n1. **429 错误增长率下降**: 4.9% → 2.4%\\\\n2. **工具调用 100% 稳定**: isError=true = 0\\\\n3. **深夜时段自我调节**: 系统可能受益于低流量时段\\\\n\\\\n### 429 错误趋势分析\\\\n```\\\\n04:00 → 764 次 (基准)\\\\n08:00 → 798 次 (+4.5%)\\\\n12:00 → 833 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n16:00 → 870 次 (+4.4%)\\\\n20:00 → 913 次 (+4.9%)\\\\n00:00 → 935 次 (+2.4%) ⬅️ 增长率下降 ✅\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n### 紧急行动\\\\n1. **充值 API 账户**（智谱 AI GLM-5）- 最紧急\\\\n2. 调查网络错误恶化原因\\\\n3. 利用深夜时段进行系统维护\\\\n\\\\n### 预测\\\\n如果充值：\\\\n- **充值后 4h**: ~50 次（-95%）\\\\n- **充值后 8h**: ~10 次（-99%）\\\\n\\\"}],\\\"isError\\\":false,\\\"timestamp\\\":1772137840318}}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"message\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"2c9905d3\\\",\\\"parentId\\\":\\\"77963c81\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-02-27T04:33:25.006Z\\\",\\\"message\\\":{\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"thinking\\\",\\\"thinking\\\":\\\"很好！我创建了一个系统健康编排器Skill。现在让我创建配套的执行脚本。\\\",\\\"thinkingSignature\\\":\\\"reasoning_content\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"### C. 生成系统健康检查脚本\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_5a0ea8bb767a4de6ad271729\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"write\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"path\\\":\\\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"#!/bin/bash\\\\n# system-health-check.sh - 系统健康统一检查脚本\\\\n# 创建时间: 2026-02-27 12:30 (Round 248)\\\\n# 用途: 统一执行所有健康检查，生成综合报告\\\\n\\\\nset -euo pipefail\\\\n\\\\n# 颜色定义\\\\nRED='\\\\\\\\033[0;31m'\\\\nGREEN='\\\\\\\\033[0;32m'\\\\nYELLOW='\\\\\\\\033[1;33m'\\\\nBLUE='\\\\\\\\033[0;34m'\\\\nCYAN='\\\\\\\\033[0;36m'\\\\nNC='\\\\\\\\033[0m'\\\\n\\\\n# 配置\\\\nSCRIPT_DIR=\\\\\\\"$(cd \\\\\\\"$(dirname \\\\\\\"${BASH_SOURCE[0]}\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\" && pwd)\\\\\\\"\\\\nREPORT_DIR=\\\\\\\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/health-reports\\\\\\\"\\\\nTIMESTAMP=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d_%H%M')\\\\nMODE=\\\\\\\"${1:-full}\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n# 日志函数\\\\nlog() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${BLUE}[$(date '+%H:%M:%S')]${NC} $1\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nlog_success() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${GREEN}✅ $1${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nlog_warning() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${YELLOW}⚠️  $1${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nlog_error() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${RED}❌ $1${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nlog_info() {\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${CYAN}ℹ️  $1${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n# 创建报告目录\\\\nmkdir -p \\\\\\\"$REPORT_DIR\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\necho \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"🏥 系统健康统一检查\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"时间: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"模式: $MODE\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\necho \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n# 初始化评分\\\\nTOTAL_SCORE=8.0\\\\nRESOURCE_SCORE=0\\\\nAPI_SCORE=0\\\\nLOG_SCORE=0\\\\nMAINTENANCE_SCORE=0\\\\n\\\\n### 模块 1: 资源检查\\\\ncheck_resources() {\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"📦 检查系统资源...\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 磁盘检查\\\\n  DISK_USAGE=$(df -h / | awk 'NR==2 {print $5}' | tr -d '%')\\\\n  DISK_AVAIL=$(df -h / | awk 'NR==2 {print $4}')\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  磁盘使用率: ${DISK_USAGE}% (${DISK_AVAIL} 可用)\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $DISK_USAGE -lt 70 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"磁盘状态: 优秀 (< 70%)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif [[ $DISK_USAGE -lt 80 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"磁盘状态: 良好 (70-80%)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  elif [[ $DISK_USAGE -lt 85 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"磁盘状态: 一般 (80-85%)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"磁盘状态: 警告 (> 85%)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 内存检查\\\\n  MEM_AVAIL=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $7}')\\\\n  MEM_TOTAL=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $2}')\\\\n  MEM_USAGE=$((100 - (MEM_AVAIL * 100 / MEM_TOTAL)))\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  内存可用: ${MEM_AVAIL}MB / ${MEM_TOTAL}MB (${MEM_USAGE}% 使用)\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $MEM_AVAIL -gt 1000 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"内存状态: 优秀 (> 1GB)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif [[ $MEM_AVAIL -gt 500 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"内存状态: 良好 (500MB-1GB)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  elif [[ $MEM_AVAIL -gt 200 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"内存状态: 一般 (200-500MB)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"内存状态: 警告 (< 200MB)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # CPU 检查\\\\n  CPU_LOAD=$(uptime | awk -F'load average:' '{print $2}' | awk '{print $1}' | tr -d ',')\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  CPU 负载: ${CPU_LOAD}\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$CPU_LOAD < 0.5\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"CPU 状态: 优秀 (< 0.5)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$CPU_LOAD < 1.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"CPU 状态: 良好 (0.5-1.0)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$CPU_LOAD < 2.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"CPU 状态: 一般 (1.0-2.0)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"CPU 状态: 警告 (> 2.0)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # Swap 检查\\\\n  SWAP_TOTAL=$(free -m | awk '/Swap:/ {print $2}')\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  Swap 配置: ${SWAP_TOTAL}MB\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $SWAP_TOTAL -eq 0 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"未配置 Swap - 建议配置 2GB\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"Swap 已配置\\\\\\\"\\\\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 计算资源评分 (满分 10)\\\\n  RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE * 10 / 20))\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  资源模块评分: ${RESOURCE_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 模块 2: API 检查\\\\ncheck_apis() {\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"🔌 检查 API 健康状态...\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查最近的 429 错误\\\\n  RECENT_429=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \\\\\\\"*.jsonl\\\\\\\" -mmin -60 -exec grep -l \\\\\\\"429\\\\\\\" {} \\\\\\\\; 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  最近 1 小时 429 错误: ${RECENT_429} 次\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $RECENT_429 -eq 0 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"API 限流: 无\\\\\\\"\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif [[ $RECENT_429 -lt 5 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"API 限流: 轻微 (< 5 次)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  elif [[ $RECENT_429 -lt 10 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"API 限流: 中等 (5-10 次)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"API 限流: 严重 (> 10 次)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE - 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查网络健康（如果有脚本）\\\\n  if [[ -f \\\\\\\"$SCRIPT_DIR/network-health-check.sh\\\\\\\" ]]; then\\\\n    log \\\\\\\"  运行网络健康检查...\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n    # 简化的 API 检查（不实际调用 API）\\\\n    API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE + 3))\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"API 端点检查: 跳过（避免触发限流）\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 计算 API 评分 (满分 10)\\\\n  API_SCORE=$((API_SCORE * 10 / 8))\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  API 模块评分: ${API_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 模块 3: 日志分析\\\\nanalyze_logs() {\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"📊 分析系统日志...\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查最近的错误日志\\\\n  RECENT_ERRORS=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \\\\\\\"*.jsonl\\\\\\\" -mmin -60 -exec grep -l '\\\\\\\"isError\\\\\\\":true' {} \\\\\\\\; 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\\\\n\\\\n  ERROR_RATE=$(echo \\\\\\\"scale=2; $RECENT_ERRORS / 1\\\\\\\" | bc)\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  最近 1 小时错误 Session: ${RECENT_ERRORS}\\\\\\\"\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  错误率: ${ERROR_RATE}/h\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $RECENT_ERRORS -eq 0 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"错误率: 优秀 (0/h)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    LOG_SCORE=10\\\\n  elif [[ $RECENT_ERRORS -lt 5 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"错误率: 良好 (< 5/h)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    LOG_SCORE=8\\\\n  elif [[ $RECENT_ERRORS -lt 10 ]]; then\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"错误率: 一般 (5-10/h)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    LOG_SCORE=6\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"错误率: 警告 (> 10/h)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    LOG_SCORE=3\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  日志模块评分: ${LOG_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 模块 4: 维护状态\\\\ncheck_maintenance() {\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"🔧 检查维护状态...\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查最近的清理记录\\\\n  LAST_CLEANUP=$(find /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory -name \\\\\\\"disk-cleanup-report-*.md\\\\\\\" -mtime -1 2>/dev/null | head -1)\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ -n \\\\\\\"$LAST_CLEANUP\\\\\\\" ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"最近清理: $(basename $LAST_CLEANUP)\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"最近清理: > 24 小时前\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 2))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 检查旧日志数量\\\\n  OLD_LOGS=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \\\\\\\"*.jsonl\\\\\\\" -mtime +7 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\\\\n\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  超过 7 天的日志: ${OLD_LOGS} 个\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $OLD_LOGS -eq 0 ]]; then\\\\n    log_success \\\\\\\"日志管理: 优秀\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 5))\\\\n  elif [[ $OLD_LOGS -lt 10 ]]; then\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"日志管理: 良好\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 3))\\\\n  else\\\\n    log_warning \\\\\\\"日志管理: 需要清理\\\\\\\"\\\\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 1))\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  # 计算维护评分 (满分 10)\\\\n  MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE * 10 / 10))\\\\n  log \\\\\\\"  维护模块评分: ${MAINTENANCE_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 计算总分\\\\ncalculate_total() {\\\\n  # 加权平均\\\\n  TOTAL_SCORE=$(echo \\\\\\\"scale=1; ($RESOURCE_SCORE * 0.3 + $API_SCORE * 0.3 + $LOG_SCORE * 0.2 + $MAINTENANCE_SCORE * 0.2)\\\\\\\" | bc)\\\\n\\\\n  # 限制范围\\\\n  if (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE > 10\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    TOTAL_SCORE=10\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE < 0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    TOTAL_SCORE=0\\\\n  fi\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 生成报告\\\\ngenerate_report() {\\\\n  calculate_total\\\\n\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"📊 系统健康总评\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 确定等级\\\\n  if (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 9.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🟢 优秀\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"✨\\\\\\\"\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 7.5\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🟢 良好\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"✅\\\\\\\"\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 6.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🟡 一般\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"⚠️\\\\\\\"\\\\n  elif (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 4.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🟠 警告\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"❗\\\\\\\"\\\\n  else\\\\n    GRADE=\\\\\\\"🔴 危险\\\\\\\"\\\\n    GRADE_EMOJI=\\\\\\\"🚨\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  echo -e \\\\\\\"${GRADE_EMOJI} 健康评分: ${TOTAL_SCORE}/10 ${GRADE}\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"模块评分:\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"  - 资源: ${RESOURCE_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"  - API: ${API_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"  - 日志: ${LOG_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"  - 维护: ${MAINTENANCE_SCORE}/10\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 生成建议\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"建议:\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $DISK_USAGE -gt 80 ]]; then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ⚠️  运行磁盘清理: $SCRIPT_DIR/system-log-cleanup.sh\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $MEM_AVAIL -lt 300 ]]; then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ⚠️  配置 Swap: sudo $SCRIPT_DIR/configure-swap.sh\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $RECENT_429 -gt 5 ]]; then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ⚠️  检查 API 余额: $SCRIPT_DIR/api-balance-monitor.sh\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  if [[ $OLD_LOGS -gt 10 ]]; then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ⚠️  清理旧日志: find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name '*.jsonl' -mtime +7 -delete\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  if (( $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE >= 9.0\\\\\\\" | bc -l) )); then\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  ${GREEN}✅ 系统状态优秀，无需改进${NC}\\\\\\\"\\\\n  fi\\\\n\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n  echo \\\\\\\"=========================================\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  # 保存报告\\\\n  REPORT_FILE=\\\\\\\"$REPORT_DIR/health-check-${TIMESTAMP}.md\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n  cat > \\\\\\\"$REPORT_FILE\\\\\\\" <<EOF\\\\n# 系统健康检查报告\\\\n\\\\n**时间**: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\\\\n**健康评分**: ${TOTAL_SCORE}/10 ${GRADE}\\\\n\\\\n## 模块评分\\\\n\\\\n- 资源: ${RESOURCE_SCORE}/10\\\\n- API: ${API_SCORE}/10\\\\n- 日志: ${LOG_SCORE}/10\\\\n- 维护: ${MAINTENANCE_SCORE}/10\\\\n\\\\n## 系统状态\\\\n\\\\n- 磁盘: ${DISK_USAGE}% (${DISK_AVAIL} 可用)\\\\n- 内存: ${MEM_AVAIL}MB 可用\\\\n- CPU: ${CPU_LOAD} 负载\\\\n- 429 错误: ${RECENT_429} 次/h\\\\n- 错误率: ${ERROR_RATE}/h\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n生成时间: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\\\\nEOF\\\\n\\\\n  log_info \\\\\\\"报告已保存: $REPORT_FILE\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\n### 主执行流程\\\\ncase \\\\\\\"$MODE\\\\\\\" in\\\\n  --quick)\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"快速检查模式\\\\\\\"\\\\n    check_resources\\\\n    check_apis\\\\n    generate_report\\\\n    ;;\\\\n\\\\n  --full)\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"完整检查模式\\\\\\\"\\\\n    check_resources\\\\n    check_apis\\\\n    analyze_logs\\\\n    check_maintenance\\\\n    generate_report\\\\n    ;;\\\\n\\\\n  --module)\\\\n    MODULE=\\\\\\\"${2:-all}\\\\\\\"\\\\n    log_info \\\\\\\"单模块检查: $MODULE\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n    case \\\\\\\"$MODULE\\\\\\\" in\\\\n      resource)\\\\n        check_resources\\\\n        ;;\\\\n      api)\\\\n        check_apis\\\\n        ;;\\\\n      log)\\\\n        analyze_logs\\\\n        ;;\\\\n      maintenance)\\\\n        check_maintenance\\\\n        ;;\\\\n      *)\\\\n        log_error \\\\\\\"未知模块: $MODULE\\\\\\\"\\\\n        echo \\\\\\\"可用模块: resource, api, log, maintenance\\\\\\\"\\\\n        exit 1\\\\n        ;;\\\\n    esac\\\\n    ;;\\\\n\\\\n  *)\\\\n    log_error \\\\\\\"未知模式: $MODE\\\\\\\"\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"使用方法:\\\\\\\"\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  $0 --quick       快速检查\\\\\\\"\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  $0 --full        完整检查\\\\\\\"\\\\n    echo \\\\\\\"  $0 --module <name>  单模块检查\\\\\\\"\\\\n    exit 1\\\\n    ;;\\\\nesac\\\\n\\\\n# 返回健康评分作为退出码（0-10）\\\\nexit $(echo \\\\\\\"$TOTAL_SCORE\\\\\\\" | awk '{print int($1)}')\\\\n\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_59dbcf4ec6614088bfb96dd8\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"chmod +x /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh\\\"}}],\\\"api\\\":\\\"openai-completions\\\",\\\"provider\\\":\\\"zai\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"glm-5\\\",\\\"usage\\\":{\\\"input\\\":2499,\\\"output\\\":3717,\\\"cacheRead\\\":67328,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"totalTokens\\\":73544,\\\"cost\\\":{\\\"input\\\":0,\\\"output\\\":0,\\\"cacheRead\\\":0,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"total\\\":0}},\\\"stopReason\\\":\\\"toolUse\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1772166713098}}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"message\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"a36d5371\\\",\\\"parentId\\\":\\\"2fbd56db\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-02-27T08:30:39.934Z\\\",\\\"message\\\":{\\\"role\\\":\\\"assistant\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"thinking\\\",\\\"thinking\\\":\\\"系统状态分析：\\\\n- 健康评分：8.5/10（良好）\\\\n- 429 错误：0（稳定）\\\\n- 内存使用波动：1.6GB → 583MB（新发现 PAT-036）\\\\n- CPU 负载略高：0.00 → 0.22（轻微）\\\\n- 最近 6 小时有 17 个活跃 session\\\\n- 最近 1 小时有 7 个 session 包含错误\\\\n\\\\n让我深入分析一下错误情况，并寻找改进机会。\\\",\\\"thinkingSignature\\\":\\\"reasoning_content\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"## Phase 2: 深度分析\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_46a09523717c4ee3bcfa566f\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"ps aux | grep -E \\\\\\\"openclaw|node\\\\\\\" | grep -v grep | head -10\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_4a4c9b0cdd15435fba594423\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \\\\\\\"*.jsonl\\\\\\\" -mmin -360 -exec grep -h \\\\\\\"isError.*true\\\\\\\" {} \\\\\\\\; 2>/dev/null | head -20\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_70b6dbb4582d47ee80055009\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"ls -lh /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/*.sh | wc -l && echo \\\\\\\"---\\\\\\\" && ls /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/*/SKILL.md | wc -l\\\"}}],\\\"api\\\":\\\"openai-completions\\\",\\\"provider\\\":\\\"zai\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"glm-5\\\",\\\"usage\\\":{\\\"input\\\":1763,\\\"output\\\":260,\\\"cacheRead\\\":83392,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"totalTokens\\\":85415,\\\"cost\\\":{\\\"input\\\":0,\\\"output\\\":0,\\\"cacheRead\\\":0,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"total\\\":0}},\\\"stopReason\\\":\\\"toolUse\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1772181027063}}\",\"cwd\":\"/root/.openclaw/workspace\"},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1772181039993}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"bad840da\",\"parentId\":\"a99a09df\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-27T20:00:42.773Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_86de699d994a449284c01c41\",\"toolName\":\"exec\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"=== 错误类型统计 ===\\n      4 \\\"error\\\":\\\"Could not find the exact text in /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/pattern-registry.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\\"\\n      3 \\\"error\\\":\\\"gateway timeout after 10000ms\\\\nGateway target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789\\\\nSource: local loopback\\\\nConfig: /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\\\\nBind: loopback\\\"\\n      2 \\\"error\\\":\\\"aborted\\\"\\n      1 \\\"error\\\":\\\"Unknown subagent target: 7baede17-13cc-467a-8681-fa4e61ee9627\\\"\\n      1 \\\"error\\\":\\\"Unknown subagent target: 5f231889-b329-4796-83b3-ecc58976116c\\\"\\n      1 \\\"error\\\":\\\"ENOENT: