ts({ action: 'list' });\n   if (active.find(a => a.id === targetId)) {\n     await subagents({ action: 'kill', target: targetId });\n   }\n   ```\n\n### 本周执行 (P2)\n\n1. **改进 Edit 工具使用**\n   - 编辑前总是先读取最新内容\n   - 考虑使用 write 替代 edit\n\n2. **统一路径配置**\n   - 创建路径常量文件\n   - 避免硬编码路径\n\n---\n\n## 📋 行动清单\n\n- [ ] 增加 Gateway 超时到 30 秒\n- [ ] 改进子代理 kill 前的存在性检查\n- [ ] 编辑文件前先读取最新内容\n- [ ] 统一 pattern-registry.md 路径配置\n\n---\n\n## 📝 模式注册\n\n新增模式已添加到 pattern-registry:\n- PAT-036: Gateway 连接超时\n- PAT-037: 任务被中断 (Aborted)\n- PAT-038: Unknown Subagent Target\n- PAT-039: Edit 工具精确匹配失败（持续）\n- PAT-040: 文件不存在 (ENOENT)\n\n---\n\n## 📊 历史对比\n\n| 指标 | Round 225 | Round 226 | Round 227 (本次) | 趋势 |\n|------|-----------|-----------|------------------|------|\n| 健康评分 | 6.0 | 7.5 | 8.5 | ⬆️ +1.0 |\n| 429 错误 | 872+ | 20 | 0 | ⬆️ 完全恢复 |\n| Network Error | 30+ | 0 | 0 | ✅ 稳定 |\n| Gateway 超时 | 0 | 0 | 3 | ⬇️ 新问题 |\n| Aborted | 5 | 1 | 2 | ⬇️ 轻微增加 |\n| Edit 失败 | 7+ | 7+ | 7 | ✅ 稳定 |\n\n---\n\n**报告生成时间**: 2026-02-28 04:00:00\n**下次分析时间**: 2026-02-28 10:00:00\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_528e0fea7e2d4ee28731f509","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查找最新的 round 目录\nLATEST_ROUND=$(ls -d /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-* 2>/dev/null | sort -t'-' -k2 -n | tail -1)\nif [ -n \"$LATEST_ROUND\" ]; then\n  LATEST_NUM=$(basename \"$LATEST_ROUND\" | grep -oE '[0-9]+' | head -1)\n  NEXT_NUM=$((LATEST_NUM + 1))\n  echo \"Latest: round-$LATEST_NUM, Next: round-$NEXT_NUM\"\nelse\n  echo \"No rounds found, creating round-227\"\n  NEXT_NUM=227\nfi\n\n# 创建新 round\nNEW_ROUND=\"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-${NEXT_NUM}-20260228-0400\"\nmkdir -p \"$NEW_ROUND\"\necho \"Created: $NEW_ROUND\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":53130,"output":2386,"cacheRead":15936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71452,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","t