{"type":"message","id":"ee71401e","parentId":"e42062ae","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:03:27.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"日志分析任务已完成。让我总结一下发现的问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ Round 255 深度日志分析已完成\n\n### 📊 分析摘要\n\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| 日志文件 | 14 个 (4.8 MB) |\n| 分析时段 | 6 小时 (10:00 - 16:00) |\n| 健康评分 | **5.5/10** 🔴 需要立即关注 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔴 严重警告：系统持续恶化\n\n| 问题 | Round 254 | Round 255 | 变化 |\n|------|-----------|-----------|------|\n| **429 错误** | 76 | 131 | ⬆️ +55 (+72%) |\n| **Gateway 超时** | 12 | 16 | ⬆️ +4 |\n| **Unknown subagent** | 26 | 36 | ⬆️ +10 |\n| **network_error** | 20 | 28 | ⬆️ +8 |\n| **aborted** | 26 | 35 | ⬆️ +9 |\n| **Gateway 内存** | 651 MB | 1,376 MB | ⬆️ +725 MB |\n\n---\n\n### 🚨 紧急行动建议\n\n1. **检查 API 余额** - 429 错误激增 72%\n2. **增加 Gateway 超时到 30 秒**\n3. **考虑 Gateway 重启** - 内存增长 725 MB（可能内存泄漏）\n4. **降低 cron 任务频率**\n\n---\n\n### 📝 生成文件\n\n- **详细报告**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-02-28-1600.md`\n- **Evolution History**: `round-255-20260228-1600/summary.md`\n- **模式注册**: 已更新 PAT-048 ~ PAT-053 状态\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 系统状态\n\n- **健康评分**: 5.5/10 (🔴 需要立即关注)\n- **上次评分**: 6.5/10 (Round 254)\n- **变化**: -1.0 ⬇️\n- **主要风险**: 429 错误激增、Gateway 内存泄漏\n\n---\n\n**下次分析时间**: 2026-02-28 20:00 PM\n**优先级**: 🔴 高 - 建议立即执行修复操作"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1919,"output":540,"cacheRead":113920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116379,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772265784952}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd92e565","parentId":"ee71401e","timestamp":"2026-02-28T12:00:01.622Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Saturday, February 28th, 2026 — 8:00 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772280001618}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e75dc20","parentId":"dd92e565","timestamp":"2026-02-28T12:00:32.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求执行新一轮深度日志分析（20:00 PM），分析最近 6 小时的日志。我需要：\n\n1. 分析最近6小时的session日志\n2. 识别错误模式、性能问题、API问题、配置问题\n3. 生成报告文件\n4. 更新evolution-history\n5. 更新pattern-registry.md（如果有新模式）\n\n让我开始执行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"执行新一轮深度日志分析（20:00 PM），分析最近 6 小时的日志。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_849e781ce14e497793ad1299","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 分析最近6小时内的session日志\necho \"=== 深度日志分析 - $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S') ===\"\n\n# 获取最近6小时的文件列表\necho -e \"\\n--- 最近6小时的 Session 日志 ---\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -newermt \"6 hours ago\" -exec ls -lh {} \\; 2>/dev/null | sort -k6,7\n\necho -e \"\\n--- 统计信息 ---\"\nFILES=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -newermt \"6 hours ago\" 2>/dev/null)\necho \"日志文件数量: $(echo \"$FILES\" | wc -l)\"\necho \"总大小: $(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs du -ch 2>/dev/null | tail -1)\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9fbfd421812841bd91ffe29b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"FILES=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -newermt \"6 hours ago\" 2>/dev/null)\n\necho \"=== 错误类型统计 ===\"\necho \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -ohE '\"error\":\\s*\"[^\"]*\"' 2>/dev/null | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -20\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 工具失败统计 ===\"\necho \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -ohE '\"tool\":\\s*\"[^\"]*\"' 2>/dev/null | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -10\n\necho -e \"\\n=== isError 统计 ===\"\necho \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -c '\"isError\":true' 2>/dev/null | grep -v \":0$\" | head -10\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 429/Rate Limit 分析 ===\"\nTOTAL_429=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -c \"429\" 2>/dev/null | awk -F: '{sum+=$2} END {print sum+0}')\necho \"总 429 错误数: $TOTAL_429\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f25e7c15a4da4e1a93e793e3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 系统资源检查\necho \"=== 系统资源检查 ===\"\ndf -h / | awk 'NR==2 {print \"磁盘使用率:\", $5, \"可用:\", $4}'\nfree -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print \"内存可用:\", $7, \"MB\"}'\nuptime | awk -F'load average:' '{print \"CPU 负载:\", $2}'\n\necho -e \"\\n=== Gateway 状态 ===\"\nps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print \"Gateway 内存:\", $6/1024, \"MB\", \"CPU:\", $3\"%\"}'\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 超时分析 ===\"\nFILES=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -newermt \"6 hours ago\" 2>/dev/null)\nTIMEOUT_COUNT=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"timeout\\|Timeout\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"超时相关记录: $TIMEOUT_COUNT\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== Gateway 超时检查 ===\"\nGW_TIMEOUT=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"gateway timeout\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"Gateway 超时: $GW_TIMEOUT\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 子代理问题检查 ===\"\nSUBAGENT_COUNT=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"Unknown subagent\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"Unknown subagent: $SUBAGENT_COUNT\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 网络错误检查 ===\"\nNET_ERROR=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"network_error\\|Network Error\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"网络错误: $NET_ERROR\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== Aborted 检查 ===\"\nABORTED_COUNT=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"aborted\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"Aborted 记录: $ABORTED_COUNT\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":106475,"output":1037,"cacheRead":10112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117624,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772280001620}}
