{"type":"compaction","id":"3027adc3","parentId":"59d34426","timestamp":"2026-02-28T16:01:15.834Z","summary":"## Goal\nExecute a scheduled deep log analysis task (cron: evolver-log-analysis) to:\n- Analyze session logs from the last 6 hours at `/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl`\n- Identify error patterns, performance issues, API failures, and configuration problems\n- Generate a detailed report file with severity-graded findings\n- Update evolution-history with a new round summary\n- Update pattern-registry.md with any new error patterns discovered\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Analyze the full 6-hour window, not just recent 30 minutes\n- Focus on: errors, warnings, timeouts, API failures (401/403/429/500), resource anomalies\n- Report problems by severity (P0/P1/P2/P3)\n- Provide specific, actionable fix recommendations\n- Do not give superficial \"system stable\" reports - dig deep for issues\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Round 254 analysis completed (11 log files, 3.9 MB, 06:00-12:00 timeframe)\n- [x] Identified critical issue surges: 429 errors (~76), Gateway timeouts (12), Unknown subagent (26), Network errors (20), Task aborted (26)\n- [x] Generated detailed report: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-02-28-1200.md`\n- [x] Created evolution-history round: `round-254-20260228-1200/summary.md`\n- [x] Updated pattern-registry.md with 6 new patterns (PAT-048 through PAT-053)\n- [x] System health score: 6.5/10 (dropped from 8.5 - needs attention)\n- [x] Positive finding: Memory improved from 684 MB → 1,618 MB (+934 MB)\n\n### In Progress\n- None - Round 254 analysis completed\n\n### Blocked\n- None\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Health Score 6.5/10**: Dropped from 8.5 due to multiple error surges; system needs attention\n- **New Patterns Registered (PAT-048 to PAT-053)**:\n  - PAT-048: 429 rate limit surge (~76 occurrences) - P0\n  - PAT-049: Gateway timeout surge (12) - P0\n  - PAT-050: Unknown subagent surge (26) - P1\n  - PAT-051: Network error surge (20) - P1\n  - PAT-052: Task aborted surge (26) - P1\n  - PAT-053: EISDIR error (1) - P2\n- **Urgent Recommendations**: Check API balance (429 errors), increase Gateway timeout to 30s, reduce cron frequency\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Urgent**: Investigate 429 rate limit surge - check API balance\n2. **Urgent**: Increase Gateway timeout from 10s to 30s\n3. **Urgent**: Reduce cron task frequency to lower concurrent pressure\n4. Next scheduled analysis: 2026-02-28 16:00 PM\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Pattern Registry**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/pattern-registry.md` (53 patterns, 35 resolved, 18 high-risk/monitoring)\n- **Current Round**: 254\n- **Key Error Surges**:\n  - 429 rate limit: `error: 429` - ~76 occurrences (P0)\n  - Gateway timeout: `gateway timeout after 10000ms\\nGateway target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789` - 12 occurrences\n  - Unknown subagent: `Unknown subagent target:` - 26 occurrences\n  - Network error: `network_error` - 20 occurrences\n- **System Status**: 6.5/10 health (🟡 needs attention), 22 Skills, memory significantly improved\n- **Reports Generated**:\n  - `log-analysis-2026-02-28-1200.md` (latest)\n  - `log-analysis-2026-02-28-0800.md`\n  - `log-analysis-2026-02-28-0400.md`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\nExecute a deep log analysis task (cron-triggered) to proactively discover issues in the OpenClaw system. Analyze the last 6 hours of session logs from `/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl` and generate a comprehensive report.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Analyze logs from the **last 6 hours** (not just recent 30 minutes)\n- Focus on: errors, warnings, timeouts, API failures, resource anomalies\n- Generate report file: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md`\n- Report format: Statistics → Issues (P0/P1/P2/P3) → Details → Recommendations\n- Update evolution-history at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/`\n- Update pattern-registry.md if new patterns discovered\n- Must actively dig for potential issues, not just report \"system stable\"\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Identified 14 log files in last 6 hours (4.8MB total)\n- [x] Collected error type statistics\n- [x] Checked system resources (disk 72%, memory 876MB available, CPU load low)\n- [x] Found Gateway status (1376.11 MB memory, 12.7% CPU)\n- [x] Counted error categories:\n  - 429 errors: 128 total\n  - Gateway timeouts: 16\n  - Unknown subagent: 36\n  - Network errors: 28\n  - Aborted: 35\n  - Edit failures: 4\n  - ENOENT errors: 1\n- [x] Analyzed 429 error time distribution (peaks at 04:00 and 00:00 hours)\n- [x] Identified high-frequency error sessions (top: 307f236a... with 186 errors)\n- [x] Retrieved previous log analysis reports for comparison\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Generate the full log analysis report file\n- [ ] Update pattern-registry.md with new patterns\n- [ ] Update evolution-history\n\n### Blocked\n- None identified\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Analysis approach**: Using grep-based keyword search combined with targeted file reading for detailed analysis\n- **Error classification**: Categorizing by severity (P0/P1/P2/P3) based on impact and frequency\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Generate comprehensive log analysis report at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-02-28-1600.md`\n2. Document discovered issues with severity ratings\n3. Update pattern-registry.md with any new patterns (PAT-048+)\n4. Update evolution-history with this round's findings\n5. Provide actionable improvement recommendations\n\n## Critical Context\n- **System Health Score**: ~8.5/10 (good condition)\n- **Key Issues Found**:\n  - 429 Rate Limit errors increasing (128 total, up from 76 in previous analysis)\n  - Gateway timeout issues (16 occurrences)\n  - Unknown subagent errors (36 occurrences)\n  - Network errors (28 occurrences)\n  - Edit tool matching failures (pattern-registry.md, HEARTBEAT.md)\n- **Error Sessions**: Top