{"type":"message","id":"5cc7dc6c","parentId":"3027adc3","timestamp":"2026-02-28T16:01:16.030Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bdd4f71b-65a8-4b51-a0ce-958f1d38e48d evolver-log-analysis] 执行深度日志分析任务（主动发现问题）：\n\n## 分析范围\n- 读取 Session 日志：/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- 分析最近 **6 小时**内的所有日志（不要只看最近 30 分钟）\n- 特别关注：错误、警告、timeout、API 失败、资源异常\n\n## 分析任务\n1. **错误模式识别**：找出重复出现的错误\n2. **性能问题**：识别慢响应、超时、资源瓶颈\n3. **API 问题**：401/403/429/500 等错误\n4. **配置问题**：缺少配置、配置错误\n5. **流程问题**：任务失败、重复工作、低效操作\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成报告文件**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告格式**：\n   - 分析统计（文件数、错误数、模式数）\n   - 发现的问题（按严重程度 P0/P1/P2/P3 排序）\n   - 每个问题的详细信息（出现次数、示例、影响）\n   - 改进建议（具体的修复方案）\n3. **更新 evolution-history**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/\n4. **如果有新模式**：更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是\"轻量检查\"然后说\"系统稳定\"\n- 主动深入挖掘潜在问题\n- 即使没有明显错误，也要分析是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 1st, 2026 — 12:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772294475890}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b86d548","parentId":"5cc7dc6c","timestamp":"2026-02-28T16:01:44.837Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次触发了深度日志分析任务，现在是 2026-03-01 00:00 AM。我需要分析最近 6 小时的日志并生成报告。\n\n让我开始分析。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"执行新一轮深度日志分析（2026-03-01 00:00 AM），分析最近 6 小时的日志。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_85edf77f5688426a81a84c45","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 分析最近6小时内的session日志\necho \"=== 深度日志分析 - $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S') ===\"\n\n# 获取最近6小时的文件列表\necho -e \"\\n--- 最近6小时的 Session 日志 ---\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -newermt \"6 hours ago\" -exec ls -lh {} \\; 2>/dev/null | sort -k6,7\n\necho -e \"\\n--- 统计信息 ---\"\nFILES=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -newermt \"6 hours ago\" 2>/dev/null)\necho \"日志文件数量: $(echo \"$FILES\" | wc -l)\"\necho \"总大小: $(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs du -ch 2>/dev/null | tail -1)\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5833d0c435794716879a65ee","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"FILES=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -newermt \"6 hours ago\" 2>/dev/null)\n\necho \"=== 错误类型统计 ===\"\necho \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -ohE '\"error\":\\s*\"[^\"]*\"' 2>/dev/null | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -20\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 429/Rate Limit 分析 ===\"\nTOTAL_429=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -c \"429\" 2>/dev/null | awk -F: '{sum+=$2} END {print sum+0}')\necho \"总 429 错误数: $TOTAL_429\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 429 错误时间段分布 ===\"\necho \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"429\" 2>/dev/null | grep -oE '2026-02-28T[0-9]{2}:' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_328d15ebb8884b2497490a3d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 系统资源检查\necho \"=== 系统资源检查 ===\"\ndf -h / | awk 'NR==2 {print \"磁盘使用率:\", $5, \"可用:\", $4}'\nfree -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print \"内存可用:\", $7, \"MB\"}'\nuptime | awk -F'load average:' '{print \"CPU 负载:\", $2}'\n\necho -e \"\\n=== Gateway 状态 ===\"\nps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print \"Gateway 内存:\", $6/1024, \"MB\", \"CPU:\", $3\"%\"}'\n\nFILES=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -newermt \"6 hours ago\" 2>/dev/null)\n\necho -e \"\\n=== Gateway 超时检查 ===\"\nGW_TIMEOUT=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"gateway timeout\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"Gateway 超时: $GW_TIMEOUT\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 子代理问题检查 ===\"\nSUBAGENT_COUNT=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"Unknown subagent\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"Unknown subagent: $SUBAGENT_COUNT\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 网络错误检查 ===\"\nNET_ERROR=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"network_error\\|Network Error\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"网络错误: $NET_ERROR\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== Aborted 检查 ===\"\nABORTED_COUNT=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"aborted\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"Aborted 记录: $ABORTED_COUNT\"\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 超时分析 ===\"\nTIMEOUT_COUNT=$(echo \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -h \"timeout\\|Timeout\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\necho \"超时相关记录: $TIMEOUT_COUNT\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_624fcc02774c4fbc89c3845b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查是否有新问题类型\nFILES=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -newermt \"6 hours ago\" 2>/dev/null)\n\necho \"=== 其他错误类型检查 ===\"\necho \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -ohE '\"error\":\\s*\"[^\"]*\"' 2>/dev/null | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -10\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 工具失败统计 ===\"\necho \"$FILES\" | xargs grep -ohE '\"tool\":\\s*\"[^\"]*\"' 2>/dev/null | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -10\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 高频错误 Session (本时段) ===\"\necho \"$FILES\" | xargs -I{} sh -c 'count=$(grep -c \"429\\|error\\|Error\" \"{}\" 2>/dev/null); echo \"$count {}\"' 2>/dev/null | sort -rn | head -5\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 最近日志分析报告 ===\"\nls -lht /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-*.md 2>/dev/null | head -3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":32539,"output":1242,"cacheRead":10112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43893,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772294476028}}
